text: Nunga magopu hian holiholingku, lam diinsahi angka musungku do ahu, ai dipandatdati nasida do ganup ari mandok tu ahu: Didia do Debatam? (42-12) Boasa sai tungki ho, ale tondingku, jala boasa sai rusak ho di bagasan ahu? Haposi ma Debata, ai sai na pujionku dope Ibana, hatuaon ni bohingku jala Debatangku.
